channel.title: [Delta] P. Oblivion
channel.description:
had to release i dont have time because i need good grades. i want to continue this project. if you want to see content and media here it is: Soo.. im here to introduce you Project Oblivion.. i have been working with this source sometime and i think its time to set some goals and stop free roaming, the base will be delta and will always be. The name Oblivion is taken from the Elder Scrolls IV game, its called that because Im attempting to add some content from there, Custom Quests....Some of the goals are making a reliable server with good and cool features.. an idea i have for one custom quest is that Somone hires you as a robber of a bank but you can't get the money and then you steal the booth, and you notice that the person that hired you was a guard... Progress Reduced Client from 632kb to 350kb and still going down. COMBAT Rewritten combat not rewritten completely but there is not a huge delay before hitting. Ranged need to get player following done, will do when all other skills are done Magic Deleted All magic stuff but the teles, maybe rewriting after all other skills are done. [img]http://i50.tinypic.com/1fec1u.png[/img] [img]http://i46.tinypic.com/5mlok9.png[/img] [img]http://i46.tinypic.com/34pmk1s.png[/img] [img]http://i47.tinypic.com/9hsy75.png[/img] [img]http://i45.tinypic.com/p6o7c.png[/img] [img]http://i48.tinypic.com/atsmyf.png[/img] [img]http://i47.tinypic.com/258t9vl.png[/img] [img]http://i48.tinypic.com/5oihw5.png[/img] [img]http://i46.tinypic.com/t9wt2w.png[/img] [img]http://i49.tinypic.com/ofeo1.png[/img] Log of progress from dev. thread.
7/11/12[Cooking 60% done.] 7/11/12[Firemaking 75% done, clipping missing.] 7/11/12[] 8/11/12[Fixed Dialogue Bug] 8/11/12[Cleaned process, and fixed conventions(tabbed..blabla)] 9/11/12[Separated Packets from client.] 9/11/12[Ripping some Demise content for Range.] 9/11/12[Reduced Client.java 40kbs.] 9/11/12[Separated Dialogues from client.] 10/11/12[Separated some voids from the client.] 10/11/12[Started Working on Draynor sewer, to be converted in to jail for the start..] 10/11/12[Global ObjectHandler.] 10/11/12[DialogHandler.] 12/11/12[Added more pics to the thread.] 12/11/12[Attempting to finish the jail part..] 13/11/12[Added worlmap class..] 13/11/12[Added cycle based task manager...] 14/11/12[Changed most of cluster loveing timers to taskM.] 14/11/12[added music system..] 14/11/12[added pickables..] day before release: run in cycle fishinghandler added more parts to the mainstory(lazy to upload more) Frame126 for leveling up, like real rs. added music to jail.
Here is the thread http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,581211.0.html and finally the dl, i'll add more pictures if you guys want Download link [URL=http://up.ht/TgDK2K]19-11-12.rar - 3.5 MB[/URL] Also im saying that im not too proud of this server and it has a lotta lack of conventions, i'm now continuing this project, making it better.. if you need anyhelp you can always message me. note its 3.2mb because of worldmap.bin. Its not packaged just organized, get over it. Thankks for downloading ma server :) , i hope somone can do something useful with this. ow yea the credits. DeltaScape Creator = 80% Me = 7% Other people that helped me all around (Teamrocket,Lostmyphat,Arham,RandQm and others) 13%
